<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.9.2">
<l>cāmāṟuṅ keṭumāṟun tamaruṟṟār talaittalaippey</l>
<l>tēmāṟik kiṭantalaṟṟu mivaiyeṉṉa vulakiyaṟkai</l>
<l>yāmāṟoṉ ṟaṟiyēṉnā ṉaravaṇaiyā yammāṉē</l>
<l>kūmāṟē viraikaṇṭā yaṭiyēṉaik kuṟikkoṇṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ways to die, ways to get lost – what are these that who have their people</l>
<l>pour on top of each other, being beguiled, lying, babbling? The nature of the world.</l>
<l>I don’t know any way that is possible, you on the serpent bed, father.</l>
<l>Make haste with a way that calls [me], see, taking hold of me [your] servant.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
